    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. GCI below 5% threshold, NIH prediction within 18% of experimental values, and RH < 1 at worst-case operating point. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The blood rheology input dataset (vintage 2025-09-15) predates the February 2026 model revision; re-validation of these inputs against the updated model build is planned for the next assessment cycle and does not affect the current acceptance decision.",
